ProcedureHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: PROC HPFARIMASPEC options ; 
    FORECAST options ; 
    INPUT options ; 
    ESTIMATE options ; 

The HPFARIMASPEC procedure is used to create an ARIMA (autoregressive
integrated moving average) model specification file. The output of this
procedure is an XML file that stores the intended ARIMA model specification.

StatementHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: INPUT options;

The INPUT statements specify the transfer function inputs in the model. 
A separate INPUT statement is needed for each of the transfer function inputs.
